<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('header'); %>
    <title>BWF | Register</title>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="javascripts/register.js"></script>
    <script src='https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js'></script>
  </head>
  <body class="container">
    <h3 class="center-align">Register for <a href="/" class="blue-text text-darken-4 hide-on-small-only">Bored With Friends</a><a href="/" class="blue-text text-darken-4 hide-on-med-and-up">BWF</a></h3>
    <div class="row">
      <p id="badUsername" class="center-align red-text hide">Invalid Username <i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i></p>
      <p id="takenUsername" class="center-align red-text hide">Username already taken <i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i></p>
      <div class="input-field col s10 m6 offset-m3 offset-s1">
        <input id="username" type="text" class="validate customInput" maxlength="63" onkeyup="checkusername(null);">
        <label for="username">Username</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <p id="badEmail" class="center-align red-text hide">Invalid Email Address <i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i></p>
      <p id="takenEmail" class="center-align red-text hide">Email already taken <i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i></p>
      <div class="input-field col s10 m6 offset-m3 offset-s1">
        <input id="eml" type="text" class="validate customInput" maxlength="255" onkeyup="checkemail(null);">
        <label for="eml">Email</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div id="weakPass" class="center-align red-text hide">
        <p>Invalid Password <i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i></p>
        <p>Passwords must be a mix of numbers and letters, at least 8 characters long.</p>
        <p>Special characters !@#$%^&*/._+- are also allowed</p>
      </div>
      <div class="input-field col s10 m6 offset-m3 offset-s1">
        <input id="pass1" type="password" class="validate customInput" maxlength="31" onkeyup="checkPassStrength();">
        <label for="pass1">Password</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <p id="badPassMatch" class="center-align red-text hide">Passwords do not match <i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i></p>
      <div class="input-field col s10 m6 offset-m3 offset-s1">
        <input id="pass2" type="password" class="validate customInput" maxlength="31" onkeyup="checkPassMatch();">
        <label for="pass2">Retype Password</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col offset-s1 offset-m4">
        <div class="g-recaptcha" data-sitekey="6LfVuQcUAAAAAA_A-NaI_gDOSApuYMrgOpPuhWRA"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col s3 m2 offset-s6 offset-m7">
        <a id="registerBtn" onclick="register();" class="waves-effect waves-light btn blue darken-4">Register</a>
        <div id="registerLoadingCircle" class="hide preloader-wrapper big active">
          <div class="spinner-layer spinner-blue-only">
            <div class="circle-clipper left">
              <div class="circle"></div>
            </div><div class="gap-patch">
              <div class="circle"></div>
            </div><div class="circle-clipper right">
              <div class="circle"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="terms-modal" class="modal modal-fixed-footer">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <h5 class="center-align">Terms of Use and Privacy Policy</h5>
        <p>By using Bored With Friends you agree to NOT use the application in any manner that would harm other people or involve any unsafe or illegal activity.</p>
        <p>As the Owner/Developer, I agree not to do anything creepy/illegal with your personal info. Email & passwords are safely stored and never disclosed to 3rd parties.</p>
        <p>At this time, you will NEVER be contacted regarding this application. NEVER disclose personal info to communication (emails) that might appear to be related to this application.</p>
        <p>I will do my best to provide a secure user experience. However, I am not liable for any harm associated with any usage of this application. Please use common sense.</p>
        <p>This application uses 3rd party services to enhance user experience. Their policies:</p>
        <p>Google Maps API: Users are bound by <a href="https://www.google.com/intl/en/policies/terms/" target="_blank">Googleâ€™s Terms of Service</a> and the <a href="https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <a onclick="acceptTerms();" class="modal-action modal-close waves-effect waves-green btn-flat ">Agree</a>
        <a onclick="rejectTerms();" class="modal-action modal-close waves-effect waves-green btn-flat ">Disagree</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

